### Cooldown System

#### Overview
The cooldown system is a simple mechanism to prevent actions from being taken too frequently.

#### Cooldown Class
```markdown
### Cooldown Class
#### Properties
* `cooldownDuration`: The duration of the cooldown in milliseconds.
* `lastActivation`: The timestamp of the last time the cooldown was activated.

#### Methods
* `activate()`: Activates the cooldown.
* `isReady()`: Checks if the cooldown is ready.
```

#### Cooldown Class Implementation
```javascript
class Cooldown {
  constructor(cooldownDuration) {
    this.cooldownDuration = cooldownDuration;
    this.lastActivation = 0;
  }

  activate() {
    this.lastActivation = Date.now();
  }

  isReady() {
    return Date.now() - this.lastActivation >= this.cooldownDuration;
  }
}
```

